\begin{frame}{OptimusVLA：雙記憶體視覺-語言-動作框架}
\begin{itemize}
\item 大幅加速並穩定機器人操作任務
\item 全局先驗記憶體提供任務級別先驗
\item 局部一致性記憶體強化時間連貫性
\end{itemize}
\end{frame}

 egin{frame}
 rametitle{Background: Vision-Language-Action Models}
 egin{itemize}
\item Map multimodal inputs directly to continuous robotic actions.
\item Generative policies provide highly expressive action distributions.
\item Standard methods rely on iterative denoising from isotropic noise.
\item This paradigm causes severe computational overhead and high latency.
\end{itemize}
\end{frame}

\begin{frame}{Motivation: Inference Latency and Consistency}
\begin{itemize}
\item High NFEs severely bottleneck real-time robotic control.
\item Starting from pure noise ignores valuable historical context.
\item Independent step-wise generation causes poor temporal consistency.
\item A new mechanism must bridge gaps and ensure smoothness.
\end{itemize}
\end{frame}

\begin{frame}{全局先驗記憶：任務級別檢索}
\begin{itemize}
\item 從記憶庫檢索語義相似的任務軌跡
\item 計算檢索實例的加權平均與變異數
\item 為生成策略提供精確的起始點
\item 大幅縮小與各向同性雜訊的分佈差距
\end{itemize}
\[
